snippet.title: Outrageous Grounds: The Maze Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Outrageous Grounds: The Maze is an upcoming virtual reality game for HTC Vive(Oculus Touch port also planned). OG:The Maze features unrestricted movement with armswing-based system,   puzzles, intense combat, survival, exploration and tons of dynamic items and destruction.

New videos coming soon!


Homepage: http://outrageousgrounds.com/
